methods.fillRangeChunk:
Fill a writable long chunk with pairs of range boundaries (start, endInclusive) starting from the next iterator
 position forward.

:param chunk: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableLongChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.OrderedKeyRanges>) - A writable chunk to fill
:param chunkOffset: (int) - An offset inside the chunk to the position to start writing
:return: (int) The count of ranges written (which matches 2 times the number of elements written).
